设评价指标体系，进一步调动各校和各地全面加强和改进新时代学校美育工作。 教育部：让每一个学生都能掌握1-2项艺术特长！"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ineq6/oaSsaRmEAMaCDY0MDc0OTkxIOfuzoQGMA84ywNAG3IJNDU4MDc3MjY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"181 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c2cd51975229632519669c6d65738be5_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1620655532.5311549","card_id":"Q_34453138","target":{"id":34453138,"title":"你认为最棒的前十位 iPad 应用是哪些？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/34453138","type":"question","created":1439273163,"answer_count":59,"follower_count":5262,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[26,503,73422],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"相关：你认为最棒的前十位 iOS 应用是哪些？"},"attached_info":"Cj0Ineq6/oaSsaRmEAMaBzU5ODc2MjQgy6GmrgUwATiOKUAccggzNDQ1MzEzOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"164 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/3a753bac3d6e0c280d569a7dda264552_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1620655532.5315936","card_id":"Q_378704818","target":{"id":378704818,"title":"有哪些好看的言情小说推荐?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/378704818","type":"question","created":1583943393,"answer_count":194,"follower_count":849,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1873,4105,15858,44871,124781],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"书荒中，超级喜欢追妻火葬场！！！不要虐？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ineq6/oaSsaRmEAMaCDQ2NDM1MTA4IOGdpPMFMAE40QZAHXIJMzc4NzA0ODE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"157 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1620655532.5318906","card_id":"